I check both: lion-strength > one bull's strength (alone wins) AND lion-strength < combined-strength (together the herd wins).

{"tool_calls":[{"name":"eval","args":{"form":"(let [lion-strength 11 bulls 5 bull-strength 10 combined-strength (* bulls bull-strength)] (and (> lion-strength bull-strength) (< lion-strength combined-strength)))"}}]}
<|end|>


