Question: the price in coins at which each single egg had sold?
<|end|>
<|asst|>
{"tool_calls":[{"name":"eval","args":{"form":"(let [per-day 2 days 25 total-coins 2100 total-eggs (* per-day days)] (quot total-coins total-eggs))"}}]}
<|end|>


